Repeat: k5, p5, k5, yo, p3, pass yo over the 3 purl stitches
k1, p5, ssk, k1, k2-tog, p5, k1, DI
End Row: k1, p5, ssk, k1, k2-tog, p5, k1, (k1-b, k1) in same stitch

Repeat: k2, p5, sl 2-k1-p2sso, p5, k2, DI
End Row: k2, p5, sl 2-k1-p2sso, p5, k2, (k1-b, k1) in last stitch

Repeat: M1-p, k2, ssk, p9, k2-tog, k2, M1-p, p1
M1-p, k2, ssk, p7, k2-tog, k2, M1-p, p3
End Row: M1-p, k2, ssk, p7, k2-tog, k2, M1-p, p2

Repeat: M1-p, k2, ssk, p5, k2-tog, k2, M1-p, p5
End Row: M1-p, k2, ssk, p5, k2-tog, k2, M1-p, p3

Repeat: M1-p, k2, ssk, p3, k2-tog, k2, M1-p, p7
End Row: M1-p, k2, ssk, p3, k2-tog, k2, M1-p, p4

End Row: M1-p, k2, ssk, p1, k2 tog, k2, M1-p, p5

Repeat: p5, k2, sl 1- k2 tog-psso, k2, p5, DI
End Row: p5, k2, sl 1- k2 tog-psso, k2, p5, (k1-b, k1) in last stitch

Repeat: M1-k, k1, p5, k1, sl 2-k1-p2sso, k1, p5, k1, M1-k, k1
k5, yo, p3, pass yo over the 3 purl stitches, k5, p5
End Row: k5, yo, p3, pass yo over the 3 purl stitches, k5, p3

Repeat: k2-tog, p5, k1, DI, k1, p5, ssk, k1
p5, k2, DI, k2, p5, sl 2-k1-p2sso
End Row: p5, k2, DI, k2, p5, ssk

Repeat: k2-tog, k2, M1-p, p1, M1-p, k2, ssk, p9
End Row: k2-tog, k2, M1-p, p1, M1-p, k2, ssk, p5

End Row: k2-tog, k2, M1-p, p3, M1-p, k2, ssk, p4

End Row: k2 tog, k2, M1-p, p5, M1-p, k2, ssk, p3
